text: Faisel Darwish (); born 3 July 1991) is a Saudi Arabian footballer who plays as a right-sided midfielder or wing-back for Al- Taawoun.https://www.sofascore.com/player/faisal-darwish/791560 ==Club Career== On 27 May 2018, Darwish left Al-Hilal after 4 years and signed with newly promoted side Al-Wehda.
